5. **Streaming Support** - Real-time response streaming
6. **Tool Approval** - Can require user approval for certain tools
7. **Skills/Plugins System** - AgentSkill framework for extensibility
8. **Evaluation** - AgentEvaluationExtensions for assessing agent behavior
9. **Telemetry** - OpenTelemetry integration

