### **QUICK REFERENCE - TYPICAL AGENT WITH TOOL CALLING**

```csharp
// 1. Create OpenAI ChatClient
var chatClient = new OpenAI.Chat.ChatClient("gpt-4o", apiKey)
    .AsIChatClient();

// 2. Create tools using AIFunctionFactory
var tools = new List<AITool>
{
    AIFunctionFactory.Create(
        (string query) => PerformSearch(query),
        "search",
        "Search the web for information"
    ),
    AIFunctionFactory.Create(
        (string code) => ExecuteCode(code),
        "execute_code", 
        "Execute Python code"
    )
};

// 3. Create agent with tool calling
var agent = new ChatClientAgent(chatClient);

// 4. Run agent with tools in a loop
var session = new ChatClientAgentSession();
var options = new ChatClientAgentRunOptions(
    new ChatOptions { Tools = tools }
);

var response = await agent.RunAsync(
    "Search for information about AI",
    session,
    options
);

// Agent automatically handles tool calling loop internally
```

